tags.documentation: Inductive Automation directory path. Use / as separator.
tags.name: installationPathIA

tags.documentation: Update this table when adding a new tool. Make sure the folder name also matches the name for settings to work properly.
tags.name: menu

tags.documentation: Currently only supports 'rapid-dev-dark' or 'rapid-dev-light'.
tags.name: theme

tags.documentation: Path on gateway computer to temporarily save files. Use / as separator.
tags.name: serverTempSaveLocation

eventScripts.script:
installationPath = system.tag.readBlocking("[.]../Settings/installationPathIA")[0].value
	path = installationPath +  "/Ignition/logs/wrapper.log"
	content = system.file.readFileAsString(path)
	
	if len(content) > 64000:
		result = system.tag.writeBlocking("[.]Wrapper Log" ,content[-64000:])
	
	else:
		system.tag.writeBlocking("[.]Wrapper Log",content)
